## MLP & LSTM 

Goals
-

- Get familiar with the basics of Neural Networks
- Understand and implement time series prediction with multi level perceptron based neural networks
- Understand and implement time seires prediction with LSTM (RNN).


Learning Objectives
-

- Neural networks in timeseries prediction
- Learn about Multi-level perceptrons
- Learn about Recurrent Neural Networks (RNN)
- Learn about Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM)
- Learn how MLP based timeseries prediction can be done using Pytorch
- Learn how LSTM can be implemented using Pytorch
- Implementing and running neural networks using GPU


Training Activities
-

- Run MLP with example data
- Run LSTM with example data
